(purse Includes $30,000 From The Purse Account Plus $15,000 From The State Enhancement Fund). $300 to enter. The ATBA will deduct 1 0% of all nominating and sustaining payments for clerical fees before the Stallion Stakes. The balance to be divided as follows: 50% to the winner, 20% to second, 10% to third, 5% to fourth, 3% to fifth, 2% to sixth; 10% to be paid to the nominator of s tallion. Starters to pass the entry box by the usual time of closing. Preference given to those entries that have accumulated the highest earnings with winners preferred regardless of earnings. Fillies, 120 lbs. Colts & Geldings, 124 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BEYOND AWESOME bobbled at the start, rushed to take command soon after, opened a clear margin and drew off through the lane. ARIZONA KALEI raced unhurried early, moved four-wide through the turn and finished with good energy. SCOPELLO lacked early speed, raced three-wide through the turn and was eased through the lane. THE RACE WAS HAND TIMED.
